************** Movie Reviews Sentiment Classification Using N Gram Models **************

Steps

1) Import Movie_Reviews.txt
2) Data preprocessing,
	i)   Lowecasing
	ii)  Remove special characters (, . " ! ') 
	iii) Tokenizing
	iv)  Remove stop words
	v)   Stemming
3) Apply N Gram Models
4) Calculate N Gram probabilities
5) Calculate the N-gram probability for the test movie review
7) Predict the category
	i) Suggesting best N gram model for the given data set.

